---
import { stats, sections } from './data';
---
<section class="px-6 py-14 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 flex-wrap">
      <h1 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-400">H09 · STRC Synthetic Peptide Hydrogel Evidence Package</h1>
      <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] rounded bg-emerald-500/15 text-emerald-300 border border-emerald-500/30 font-semibold">S-TIER</span>
      <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] rounded bg-cyan-500/15 text-cyan-300 border border-cyan-500/30 font-semibold">COMPUTATIONAL DOSSIER</span>
      <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] rounded bg-amber-500/15 text-amber-300 border border-amber-500/30 font-semibold">WETLAB-GATED</span>
      <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] rounded bg-neutral-500/15 text-neutral-300 border border-neutral-500/30 font-semibold">REVIEWER PACK · 2026-04-27</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-8">
      Ototopical self-assembling peptide hydrogel hypothesis for STRC-null hearing loss. The therapeutic idea is to form a synthetic horizontal top connector at the stereocilia surface using a RADA16-WH2-STRC tail91 peptide, restoring mechanical coupling without AAV, mRNA, cells, or genome editing.
    </p>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
      {stats.map((s) => (
        <div class="border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500 font-semibold mb-2">{s.label}</div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">{s.value}</div>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">{s.note}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <nav class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5" aria-label="Page sections">
      {sections.map((sec) => (
        <a href={`#${sec.id}`} class="px-2 py-1 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500 hover:text-white border border-white/5 hover:border-white/20 rounded no-underline transition-colors">{sec.label}</a>
      ))}
    </nav>
  </div>
</section>
